                  <fr:day>20</fr:day>
                </fr:date>
                <fr:anchor>7522</fr:anchor>
                <fr:addr type="user">jms-00JO</fr:addr>
                <fr:route>jms-00JO.xml</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="Pointwise addition of matrices">Pointwise addition of <fr:link href="jms-00IS.xml" title="Matrix over a semiring" addr="jms-00IS" type="local">matrices</fr:link></fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[M,N\in \mathrm {Mat}_{S}{\mathopen {}\left (m,n\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> be two <fr:link href="jms-00IS.xml" title="Matrix over a semiring" addr="jms-00IS" type="local">matrices</fr:link> over the same semiring with the same dimensions. We will write <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[M\oplus  N\in \mathrm {Mat}_{S}{\mathopen {}\left (m,n\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> for the <fr:em><fr:strong>(pointwise) addition</fr:strong></fr:em> of the two matrices:</fr:p>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
 {\mathopen {}\left (M\oplus  N\right )\mathclose {}}_{i,j} = M_{i,j} \oplus  N_{i,j}
]]></fr:tex>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
                  </fr:author>
                </fr:authors>
                <fr:date>
                  <fr:year>2024</fr:year>
                  <fr:month>1</fr:month>
                  <fr:day>20</fr:day>
                </fr:date>
                <fr:anchor>7523</fr:anchor>
                <fr:addr type="user">jms-00JP</fr:addr>
                <fr:route>jms-00JP.xml</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="The zero matrix">The zero matrix</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <fr:p>A <fr:em><fr:strong>zero <fr:link href="jms-00IS.xml" title="Matrix over a semiring" addr="jms-00IS" type="local">matrix</fr:link></fr:strong></fr:em> is one that whose cells all contain <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[0]]></fr:tex>. In particular, we have:</fr:p>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
 \begin {aligned}
   \mathbf {0} &\in  \mathrm {Mat}_{S}{\mathopen {}\left (m,n\right )\mathclose {}}\\
   \mathbf {0}_{i,j} &= 0
 \end {aligned}
]]></fr:tex>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
